				""
				"§eWhere to find one:§r"
				"§7• §eDungeon chests§7 — YUNG's and D&T structures have the best"
				"§7  chance to drop rare trinkets."
				"§7• §eBuried Treasure§7 — use a treasure map from fishing or a"
				"§7  Cartographer villager."
				"§7• §eMineshaft§7 chests — less common, but possible."
				""
				"§eCurios slots available:§r"
				"§7• §eBack§7 — cloak slot (backpacks go here)."
				"§7• §eCharm×2§7 — trinket charm slots (Lucky Charm goes here)."
				"§7• §eRing×2§7 — ring slots."
				"§7• §eHead§7 — cosmetic hat slot."
				""
				"§a► Obtain a Lucky Charm (don't need to equip it, just have it)."
			]
