		{
			x: 6.0d
			y: 44.0d
			id: "000D000D"
			tasks: [{
				id: "000D100D"
				type: "checkmark"
				title: "Locate a Stronghold and enter the room that contains the End Portal frame"
			}]
			rewards: [
				{id: "000D2010" type: "item" item: "minecraft:eye_of_ender" count: 12}
				{id: "000D2011" type: "xp" xp: 75}
			]
			title: "Ancient Stronghold"
			icon: "minecraft:ender_eye"
			description: [
				"§6The Stronghold§f is the gateway between the Overworld and The End."
				"§fLocating and entering it is the final step before the End Portal Key gate."
				""
				"§eFinding the Stronghold:§r"
				"§7• Craft §eEye of Ender§7 (Ender Pearl + Blaze Powder)."
				"§7• §eThrow it§7 (right-click) — it rises into the air pointing toward"
				"§7  the nearest Stronghold. Follow the direction it indicates."
				"§7• Throw again periodically to recalibrate. Eyes have a §e20 Enderpearl§7"
				"§7  crafting cost, so your 12-Eye reward from this quest covers filling"
				"§7  the portal."
				"§7• When the Eye drops §estraight down§7 instead of flying forward,"
				"§7  the Stronghold is directly beneath you. Dig down."
				""
				"§eNavigating the Stronghold:§r"
				"§7• Strongholds in YUNG's Better Strongholds are much larger and"
				"§7  more maze-like than vanilla. Bring a §efull stack of torches§7."
				"§7• Mark intersections as you go — the Portal Room is usually"
				"§7  deeper and in a central chamber."
				"§7• The Portal Room has a §eSilverfish spawner§7 — destroy it first."
				""
				"§eNext quest:§r"
				"§7• Once you find the Portal Room, you need §emagic (Ch 1) AND§7"
				"§7  §etechnology (Ch 2) both at gate-level§7 before you can activate it."
				"§7• The §eEnd Portal Key§7 gate below requires both Chapter gates."
				""
				"§a► Enter the Stronghold Portal Room. Mark done when you see the frame."
			]
			dependencies: ["000D000C"]
		}

