			title: "Nether Bound"
			icon: "minecraft:obsidian"
			description: [
				"§6The Nether§f in Arcane Frontiers is overhauled by §6Incendium§f,"
				"§fadding new biomes, structures, and hostile environments."
				""
				"§eBuilding a Nether Portal:§r"
				"§7• §eMinimum frame:§7 2 wide × 3 tall Obsidian (10 blocks total)."
				"§7• §eStandard frame:§7 4 wide × 5 tall for comfortable passage."
				"§7• Light with §eFlint & Steel§7 or fire charge."
				"§7• §ePortal alignment matters§7 — Nether coordinates are Overworld ÷ 8."
				"§7  Build a second portal at the Nether side (Nether x/z × 8 = Overworld)"
				"§7  to ensure reliable linking."
				""
				"§eNether survival basics:§r"
				"§7• §eFire Protection§7 enchant on armor — mandatory."
				"§7• Bring §eEnder Pearls§7 for emergency escape from cliffs."
				"§7• §eGolden Helmet§7 prevents Piglins attacking (or full Gold armor)."
				"§7• §eMilk Bucket§7 cures Wither effect from Wither Skeletons."
				""
				"§eIncendium changes:§r"
				"§7• New Nether biomes with unique terrain (see next quest)."
				"§7• New hostile mobs — read descriptions carefully in the next quests."
				"§7• §eIncendium structures§7 contain high-tier loot unavailable elsewhere."
				""
				"§a► Enter the Nether. Mark done when the loading screen completes."
			]
			dependencies: ["000D0006"]
		}

		{
			x: 24.0d
			y: 8.0d
			id: "000D0010"
