			description: [
				"§6Wither Skeleton Skulls§f are rare drops from Wither Skeletons"
				"§finside Nether Fortresses. You need three of them to summon the Wither."
				""
				"§eDropping skulls:§r"
				"§7• Default drop rate is §e2.5%§7 per kill."
				"§7• §eLooting III§7 on your sword raises it to §e5.5%§7."
				"§7• On average: 20–40 kills per skull without Looting."
				"§7• §eTip:§7 the Wither Skeleton hallways in YUNG's Fortresses contain"
				"§7  the highest density of skeletons in the pack."
				""
				"§eLooting III sources:§r"
				"§7• §eEnchanting Table§7 (30-level bookshelves) — requires XP farm."
				"§7• §eArs Nouveau§7 Enchanting Apparatus — more controlled outcomes."
				"§7• §eAnvil§7 + Looting III book from dungeon chests."
				""
				"§eThe goal: 3 skulls total§r"
				"§7• You need three for the Wither fight (quest 000D0014)."
				"§7• The §eSoul Sand§7 can be found in the Fortress basement or in"
				"§7  Soul Sand Valley — §e4 blocks§7 form the T-shape for Wither summon."
				""
				"§a► Collect 1 Wither Skeleton Skull. Mark done."
