			]
			title: "Blaze Farmer"
			icon: "minecraft:blaze_rod"
			description: [
				"§6Blaze Rods§f are one of the most important mid-game resources."
				"§fYou need them for Brewing Stands, Eyes of Ender, and more."
				""
				"§eBlaze Rods are used in:§r"
				"§7• §eBlaze Powder§7 — crafted 1:1, used in Eyes of Ender and potions."
				"§7• §eBrewng Stand§7 — requires 1 Blaze Rod + 3 Cobblestone."
				"§7• §eArs Nouveau§7 — fire glyphs scaled by Blaze Powder."
				"§7• §eFarmer's Delight§7 — Blaze Stew and other nether cuisine."
				""
				"§eEfficient Blaze farming:§r"
				"§7• Find a §eBlaze Spawner§7 in the YUNG's Fortress."
				"§7• Build a §eplatform§7 above the spawner, leave a 2-block gap."
				"§7  Blazes float up — funnel them onto your platform with a wall."
				"§7• §eCreate automation§7: a Mechanical Arm above the kill zone feeds"
				"§7  Rods into a Brass Funnel → chest automatically. See Ch 2."
				""
				"§eSafety:§r"
				"§7• §eFire Resistance potion§7 — Blaze fireballs set you on fire for 4 seconds."
				"§7• §eEnder Pearl§7 — emergency escape when surrounded."
				"§7• §eLotus Root (Farmer's Delight)§7 — fire resist food alternative."
				""
				"§a► Collect 16 Blaze Rods. They don't need to come from one trip."
			]
			dependencies: ["000D0011"]
