			title: "Nether Star"
			icon: "minecraft:nether_star"
			description: [
				"§6The Wither§f is the first major boss fight in Arcane Frontiers."
				"§fIts §eNether Star§f drop is used to craft a §eBeacon§f — the most"
				"§fpowerful passive buff structure in the game."
				""
				"§eSummoning the Wither:§r"
				"§7• You need §e3 Wither Skeleton Skulls§7 (from quest 000D0012)."
				"§7• Arrange §e4 Soul Sand blocks§7 in a T-shape (flat on ground or vertically)."
				"§7• Place §e3 Wither Skulls§7 on top of the three Soul Sand blocks."
				"§7• The Wither spawns immediately. §eBack away fast.§7"
				""
				"§eFight strategy:§r"
				"§7• §ePhase 1§7 — Wither fires Wither Skulls (blue = armor-piercing)."
				"§7  Stay mobile. §eShield§7 (or Ars Nouveau Orbit + Shield spell) blocks skulls."
				"§7• §ePhase 2§7 (below half health) — Wither gains a shield."
				"§7  §eYou must hit it in melee§7 — ranged and spells are blocked."
				"§7  This is when Tetra gear pays off — see Ch 2.7."
				"§7• §eArs Nouveau§7 — Projectile + Harm + Amplify spell hits hard in Phase 1."
				""
				"§eBattle location:§r"
				"§7• §eFight underground§7 in a hollow mine chamber."
				"§7  Wither explosion breaks most blocks — don't fight above your base!"
				"§7• §eBedrock§7 ceiling (like the Nether roof) contains Wither explosions well."
				""
				"§eNether Star uses:§r"
				"§7• §eBeacon§7 (Glass + Star + Obsidian) — gives everyone in range"
				"§7  Haste, Speed, Strength, or Regeneration. Essential for the colony."
				""
				"§a► Summon and defeat the Wither. Collect the Nether Star. Mark done."
			]
			dependencies: ["000D0012" "000D0013"]
		}

