			title: "Into The End"
			icon: "minecraft:end_stone"
			description: [
				"§6The End§f is Arcane Frontiers' final Overworld-adjacent dimension."
				"§f§6Nullscape§f has overhauled the outer End islands with new biomes"
				"§fand terrain — the center island and Dragon fight are unchanged."
				""
				"§ePreparing for The End:§r"
				"§7• §eFull Diamond armor§7 minimum. Enchant with §eProtection IV§7."
				"§7• §eEnder Pearls ×16§7 — for crossing gaps and emergency escapes."
				"§7• §eArrows ×128§7 or a §eMana bow§7 (Ars Nouveau) for the Crystals."
				"§7• §eBed§7 — §eDO NOT USE§7 in The End (explosive, kills Dragon faster"
				"§7  but also kills you)."
				"§7• §eGolden Apples ×4§7 — emergency healing."
				""
				"§eEnd Portal → Spawn platform:§r"
				"§7• You spawn on a §eObsidian pillar platform§7 above the void."
				"§7• §eDrop carefully§7 onto the main End island using Ender Pearls."
				"§7• The Dragon will be circling — don't panic. It won't dive immediately."
				""
				"§eNullscape (outer islands — Ch 3 quests 17–19):§r"
				"§7• Reach the outer islands by §ebuilding a bridge§7 from the central"
				"§7  island to the outer void. Ender Pearls can cross 20-block gaps."
				"§7• §eElytra§7 makes outer island exploration trivially easy."
				"§7  Kill the Dragon first — Elytra is only in End City ship chests."
				""
				"§a► Enter The End. Mark done when you see the central island."
			]
			dependencies: ["000D000E"]
		}

