			title: "Dragon Defeated"
			icon: "minecraft:dragon_head"
			subtitle: "The gate is yours"
			description: [
				"§6The Ender Dragon§f is the climactic combat encounter that unlocks"
				"§fthe outer End islands — and the Elytra — for the whole family."
				""
				"§eFight overview:§r"
				"§71. §eDestroy the End Crystals§7 on top of the obsidian pillars first."
				"§7   They heal the Dragon. Shoot them with bow or throw Ender Pearl."
				"§7   §eCaged crystals§7 (iron bars) — shoot the crystal through the cage."
				"§72. §eCharge attacks§7 — Dragon swoops toward you, cannot be hit mid-flight."
				"§7   Dodge sideways or use §eArs Nouveau§7 flight glyph to ascend fast."
				"§73. §ePerch phase§7 — Dragon lands on the central pillar portal."
				"§7   §eNow attack!§7 Melee the head (weak point) or charge spells."
				"§7   Tetra upgraded sword deals 8–14 damage per hit on head contact."
				"§74. §eDeath§7 — explosion, beam, massive XP drops, portal activates."
				""
				"§eArs Nouveau synergy:§r"
				"§7• §eProjectile + Harm + Amplify + Extend Time§7 deals ~60 source"
				"§7  but hits for 12 damage — excellent during the perch phase."
				"§7• §eAoeWard§7 (your Mage Spellbook) blocks Dragon Breath clouds."
				""
				"§eReward: Dragon Breath ×8§r"
				"§7• Used to craft §eLingeringPotion§7 (Tipped Arrows, area-effect traps)."
				"§7• Also an ingredient in §eArs Nouveau§7 advanced rituals."
				""
				"§a► Kill the Ender Dragon. The portal will activate automatically."
				"§a► Step through it back to the Overworld, or continue to outer islands."
			]
