				"§7• §eFall off a block§7 then §epress Jump§7 mid-air to open the wings."
				"§7• §eFirework Rockets§7 give thrust mid-flight — right-click to boost."
				"§7  Your 32 reward rockets get you started."
				"§7• §eArs Nouveau§7 — the §eFly§7 glyph provides powered flight without"
				"§7  rockets, but uses Source. Elytra gliding is free."
				""
