				"§7• §eUnbreaking III + Mending§7 — Elytra with Mending never wears out."
				"§7• §eCurse of Binding§7 — §eDO NOT put this on your Elytra§7."
				""
				"§a► Obtain the Elytra from the End Ship item frame."
