				"§eShulker Boxes in storage systems:§r"
				"§7• §eSophisticated Storage§7 (Ch 2.3) can §eautomatically sort§7 into"
				"§7  color-coded Shulker Boxes using the Sorting Upgrade."
				"§7• §eCreate§7 Mechanical Arms can move Shulker Boxes between depots."
				"§7• §eLittle Logistics§7 (Ch 2.8) — Barges can carry Shulker Boxes"
				"§7  river-to-river for bulk material transport."
				""
				"§eColony integration:§r"
